properties.title: White pit bull mix with spotted ears
properties.description:
Last seen at the intersection of San Mateo and Olive Street in South Redlands today around 9am. Very gentle but very timid 45 pound white Pit Bull mix with black spots on ears. He's a neutered male, about 3 years old. He will follow your dog into your yard, but will probably run away if you try to approach him yourself. He's wearing an orange collar that has a silver vaccine tag on it from Redlands Animal Hospital. 

His name is "Wu"
